    <h1>2017 System Programming Assignment 3</h1>
    <h3>I. Problem Description</h3>
    <p>
      The goal of this assignment is to be familiar with the concepts of signal and inter-
process communication covered in Chapter 10 and 14 in the textbook.<br> In this assignment,
you will handle the communication between parent processes and child processes
faultlessly between a web server and CGI processes.<br>
    </p>
